        <mxCell id="auoU22jt2JIBt9jpind9-1" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="set2 ). -&amp;gt;.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Design a WhatsApp system with proper following requirements :&lt;div&gt;1. User service&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Chat service&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Group Service&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Optimize the chat service for handling the millions of request . Specify the type of connection used in the design . Determine how the desgin will be done for last seen functionality . Implement CDC pipeline in the same architecture .&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="200" width="740" x="40" y="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="auoU22jt2JIBt9jpind9-2" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;aspect=fixed;fillColor=none;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;1. Functional requirements -&amp;gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. User authentication&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. one to one chatting&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Group creation, add member and removal of it .&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4.&amp;nbsp; message read double tick feature&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
